LSPR, the collective electron oscillations in limited space, can be excited in Ag cylinder, which can affect diffraction efficiency, thus influencing the ALT effect. To analyze the influence of LSPR effect, we firstly investigate the transmittance of MDCG at various cylinder radius r as shown in Fig. 4. In fact, when fixing the values of lattice period P and refractive index nl\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
